<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Acceptation invitation parent</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.3/font/bootstrap-icons.min.css">
    <style>
        body { min-height:100vh; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; background:linear-gradient(135deg, #063a55, #0b4fa3); font-family:'Segoe UI', sans-serif; padding:20px; }
        .card-i { background:#fff; border-radius:16px; padding:36px; max-width:460px; width:100%; box-shadow:0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,.3); }
        .badge-top { display:inline-block; background:#d1fae5; color:#065f46; padding:4px 12px; border-radius:20px; font-size:.75rem; font-weight:700; }
        h1 { font-size:1.4rem; font-weight:800; color:#0b1f3a; margin:12px 0 6px; }
        .form-control { background:#f8fafc; border:1.5px solid #e2e8f0; border-radius:10px; padding:11px 14px; font-size:.93rem; }
        .btn-primary-i { background:linear-gradient(135deg, #1d4ed8, #2563eb); border:none; color:#fff; font-weight:700; padding:12px; border-radius:10px; width:100%; font-size:.95rem; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="card-i">
        <span class="badge-top"><i class="bi bi-envelope-check"></i> Invitation valide</span>
        <h1>Bienvenue parent de {{ joueur.prenom }} !</h1>
        <p style="color:#64748b; font-size:.9rem; margin-bottom:24px;">
            {% if existing_user %}
                On a trouvé un compte existant avec ton email <strong>{{ invitation.emailCible }}</strong>. Le lien parent sera créé directement.
            {% else %}
                Crée ton compte parent en 30 secondes pour suivre les activités de ta fille.
            {% endif %}
        </p>

        <form method="POST">
            <input type="hidden" name="_token" value="{{ csrf_token('parent_invitation_' ~ invitation.id) }}">

            <div class="mb-3">
                <label class="small fw-semibold text-secondary">Email</label>
                <input type="email" class="form-control" value="{{ invitation.emailCible }}" disabled>
            </div>

            {% if not existing_user %}
                <div class="row g-2">
                    <div class="col-6">
                        <label class="small fw-semibold text-secondary">Prénom</label>
                        <input type="text" name="prenom" class="form-control" required autofocus>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-6">
                        <label class="small fw-semibold text-secondary">Nom</label>
                        <input type="text" name="nom" class="form-control" required>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="mb-3 mt-2">
                    <label class="small fw-semibold text-secondary">Mot de passe (8 chars min)</label>
                    <input type="password" name="password" class="form-control" required minlength="8">
                </div>
            {% endif %}

            <button type="submit" class="btn-primary-i mt-3">
                <i class="bi bi-check-circle"></i> {% if existing_user %}Accepter le lien{% else %}Créer mon compte parent{% endif %}
            </button>
        </form>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
